g.text: [there are no properties in the system]
tells the user that there are no properties in the system
request to select desired Filters to list the properties
[the user chose one or more filters]
[there are no properties in the system that meet the chosen filters]
tells the user that there are no properties in the system with those criteria
[there are properties in the system that meet
those criteria or they didn't choose any criteria]
list properties and request to select one
[if the client hasn't registered an offer for this property]
[client has sent an amount that is equal to the amount
from another client for this property]
displays: "An order with the same amount has already been registered
by another client for this property"
[if client has already registered an offer for this property]
displays: "Order already placed for this property"
